com.siperian.bdd.userexits.operations

Interface ISendForApproveOperationPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBaseOperationPlugin, ISaveOperationPlugin

    public interface ISendForApproveOperationPlugin
extends ISaveOperationPlugin

    Defines the user exits for the Send for Approval operation.

    The Send for approval operation extends the save record operation and has the same properties.

    OperationType should be set to SEND_FOR_APPROVAL_OPERATION.
